page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the JavaScript SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first chat completions call with the JavaScript SDK.
chunk_content: Install the client libraryInstall the required packages for JavaScript with npm from within the context of your new directory:```consolenpm install openai dotenv @azure/identity```Your app's _package.json_ file will be updated with the dependencies.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the setup.
